*Install Angular Command Line Interface (CLI)
    npm install -g @angular/cli@^8

*Create a new app
    ng new public

*Launch an Angular application
    ng build --watch
    
1) Create a service
    ng g s http
2) Register
    app.module.ts
        import
        [providers]
3) HttpClient
    app.module.ts
        import
        [imports]
4) Dependency Injection
    http.service.ts
        import
        attribute
    app.component.ts
        